        dmp-cli
        =======
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/dmp-cli.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/dmp-cli
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/knowsuchagency/dmp-cli.svg
